* BMAP phase-7 IF: IFE/IFG/IFL/INE compare two operands; if false the next card
* is skipped.  Assembles OCT 1 (1=1), OCT 3 (1<2), OCT 5 (1<>2); skips OCT 2,4.
       OUNAME IFTST
       IFE    1,1
       OCT    1
       IFE    1,2
       OCT    2
       IFL    1,2
       OCT    3
       IFG    1,2
       OCT    4
       INE    1,2
       OCT    5
       END
